    "description": "<p>Bistrone36 is a cosy, jovial bar and kitchen tucked away in a corner of a peaceful street situated at Whampoa West. We serve carefully crafted, well-seasoned dishes with care and attention provided. Our menus change seasonally to ensure we serve what the customers love most - fresh &amp; delicious! You’ll find well-cooked, honest uncomplicated yet creative food here in Bistrone36. Our chefs are passionate about sourcing out ingredients fresh from shelves. Our bistro is open all day for relaxed dining in peaceful surroundings, perfect for those who want to chill, to rewind or for important business meals.</p>",
